<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <title><%= title %></title>
    <link rel='stylesheet' href='/stylesheets/style.css' />
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.2.2/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" integrity="sha384-Zenh87qX5JnK2Jl0vWa8Ck2rdkQ2Bzep5IDxbcnCeuOxjzrPF/et3URy9Bv1WTRi" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.2.2/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js" integrity="sha384-OERcA2EqjJCMA+/3y+gxIOqMEjwtxJY7qPCqsdltbNJuaOe923+mo//f6V8Qbsw3" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/4.7.0/css/font-awesome.min.css">
  </head>
  <body>
    
    <div id="upper-bar">
      <div class="link" id="one"><a href="/">Cattle</a></div>
      <div class="link" id="two"><a href="/shed">Shed</a></div>
      <div class="link" id="three"><a href="/grazing">Grazing</a></div>
      <div class="link" id="four"><a href="/milk">Diary Output</a></div>
    </div>
    <br>
    <br>
    <br>
    <br>
    <br>
    <br>
    <br>
    <br>
    <br>
    <br>
    <br>
    <br>
    <br>
    <h1><%= title %></h1>
    <br>
    <br>
    <div id="text-part">
      <p>Extended grazing periods are essential for high quality diary output and peak cattle health. In order to ensure environmental standards are met, the grazing area is separated in 10 geo locations.</p>
      <p>Based on real-time tracking, a monthly overutilisation per area can be determined. Based on that, please find all areas that were overutilised below. These areas should be avoided in the next grazing period to make sure that environmental standards remain high.</p>
      <br>
      <div>
        <form action="/grazing" method="get">
          <input class="button" type="button" value="Get Grazing Trends" onclick="document.getElementById('hidden').style.display = 'block' ;"/>
        </form>
        <br>
        <button class="button"><a href="/grazingblocklist">Add animal to blocklist</a></button>
        <br>
        <br>
        <button class="button"><a href="/grazinglocation">Stream grazing live location</a></button>
        <br>
        <br>
      </div>
    </div>
    <br>
    <br>
    <br>
    <div id="hidden">
      <div id="text-part">
        <b>Grazing Information:</b>
        <br>
        <ul>
        <% if(error) { %>
          <li><%= error %></li>
        <% } else { %>
          <li>Locations to be avoided due to overutilisation: <%= avoidLocations %></li>
          <li>Locations safe to visit for the next grazing period: <%= safeLocations %></li>
        <% } %>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>